(H2. If label is [E], iterate directly over string/list items \(for item in data\).) Tj
T*
(H3. For while loops, always update control variable to avoid infinite loop.) Tj
T*
(H4. Digit logic: last = n % 10, then n //= 10.) Tj
T*
(H5. Reverse number: rev = rev*10 + last.) Tj
T*
